          "key": "reasoningSummary",
          "label": "Show Reasoning Summary",
          "type": "boolean",
        },
      ],
      "helpText": "Request a reasoning summary so the model's thinking can be shown in chat (display only; never re-fed to the model). Only the reasoning OpenAI models (GPT-5, o-series) produce one. OpenAI does not always expose a summary — if nothing appears, the model simply did not return one.",
      "title": "Reasoning",
    },
  ],
}
`;

